Hi there 
Depression cure ?
Simply cuddle a rat. 
But also tho never be afraid and never be pressured into not reaching out for help.
As a few of you know I have what is referred to as clinically severe depression - and often in winter times it’s a lot harder for a lot of people - and those symptoms can manifest in a lot of ways. 
One of the biggest ways it manifests for me is social media, even just responding to my closest loved ones becomes extremely hard and anxiety inducing. 
It can manifest in a large number of ways for different people. 
We’re trying our bests, and personally in my situation, if I don’t reach out or reply or cancel something it’s not because I’m purposefully alienating you or ignoring you, it’s just hard for me to be social or even just to be close to people (even my most loved ones) simply because it’s symptom I experience. 
Please be kind to your loved ones during the winter/fall months - it often becomes a lot harder for those who struggle with depression of any level during these months.
Even if we don’t/cant reply or reach out, it really does mean so much that you care enough to check in. 
Well wishes, strength, and courage to all of those who also struggle with their mental health in any way. 🖤
And cuddle a rat if there’s one handy🐁🖤
#rats #mentalhealth #depressionhelp

Hello hello hello 
I have not been able to be a spooky lil thing or post much for a little bit (like weeks lol) 
I got SOOOO sick, and then better for like a day or two, and then somehow got SOOOOO sick immediately with something completely different.
And then after that I had to take a little recovery time and only work a little because I was so tired and worn out from being so sick - it took me a minute to get back to feeling normal physically and mentally. I was pretty miserable.
I spent time with some family and had a long weekend and was in my pajamas most of the time (except for the drag show!)
And it’s just been kinda hard or not in my immediate interest, because I wasn’t feeling super great for awhile, (and didnt feel super great about myself) to take little videos or photos, and when I’m at work sometimes I forget cuz busy ! 
I hope everyone’s doing great so far in the new year, despite the icky it’s actually been fairly lovely. 
🎀✨🖤
I’ll do some spoopy stuff soon cuz I NEEEEEED it or I might just evaporate, but till then enjoy my complete other persona of soft baby 😂🖤
